Uses of Package
individual

  • Packages that use individual 
    Package Description
    individual
    Package related to the individuals to be used and the operations they perform or suffer.
    simulation
    Package that contains the items related with the simulation structure, i.e., the abstract class for the grid and our implementation of it, the Point class and the Edge.
  • Classes in individual used by individual 
    Class and Description
    AIndividual
    Abstract class for individuals to use, has certain needed parameters and methods to ensure the program works
    AIndividualList
    Abstract class for the individuals list.
    EvDeath
    Death event class, used to do death events, extends EvIndividual.
    EvIndividual
    Abstract class for events that are related to the individuals, needing always a reference to that individual.
    EvMove
    Move event class, used to do move events, extends EvIndividual.
    EvReproduction
    Reproduction event class, used to do reproduction events, extends EvIndividual.
    Individual
    Abstract class for the individual used.
    IndividualList
    Class for the individual list.
  • Classes in individual used by simulation 
    Class and Description
    AIndividualList
    Abstract class for the individuals list.
